&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Technical Delivery Manager post to work within the IT &amp; Information Department. The post holder will be responsible for the on-going delivery and development of Trust-wide ICT infrastructure such as PCs, laptops, mobile phones, networks and servers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The postholder must have experience in the management of enterprise level IT systems and have a good technical knowledge of industry standard networking, telecommunications and server technologies, especially VMware, AlwaysOn and other remote access technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will have experience of working with complex IT systems, management of staff, a history of delivering significant IT projects and have financial management experience including budget monitoring and cost benefit analysis. They will need to have experience of creating and developing strategies, processes, standards, policies and procedures and service level agreements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
